The app does what it says it does. Ive had no problems with this app. Easy to sign in, but the only thing i don't like is how it forces you to accept messages, i haven't had a problem though. The news is a little biased and aims to grab your attention no matter what, but then again, its the same as every other news channel.

Instead of writing a non-professional rant on how much you think trump is hitler, message me on instagram:

@Trash___man

Ill be understanding, honest, and i wont scream at you because i don't agree with your opinion, instead, i will tell you what i think, and i will tell you what i believe, maybe we can come to an understanding.
